.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-TOP-EARNERS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-top-earners \- show top channels by total routing fee earned
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-top-earners
.RB [ --limit
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Ranks channels by total fees earned from settled forwards, returning
the top
.I N
channels (default 10).
Returns an empty array if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{channel_id, total_fee_msat}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-fee-earned (1),
.BR lightning-node-fee-revenue (1)
